3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The paper deals with the analysis of a network, specifically a cellular network, and its performance. 
4. cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): The paper may be relevant to the study of multiagent systems in the context of cellular networks. 
5. cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory): The paper may be relevant to the study of game theory in the context of cellular network design and optimization.
